Compare & book cheap flight tickets on BudgetAir

   Planning a trip? If you're looking for the best quality, variety of
   flight options, and excellent service when booking an airline ticket,
   then choose BudgetAir.com.tw! We will make sure every penny you paid is
   well worth the money.

9000+ Destinations

   On BudgetAir you can choose flights to over 9000+ destinations
   worldwide. How about a weekend getaway in Hong Kong, eat, shop and get
   massage in Bangkok, or a cultural visit to countries in Europe while
   there are so many great flight deals? Whether you are planning to
   depart from Taiwan or from abroad, we strive to make the booking
   process as simple as possible, so you can start focusing on finding
   your best itinerary!

Exclusive deals on BudgetAir.com.tw

   Want great offers to your next destination? Apart from the wide variety
   of airline deals we offer you, check out our promotions for exclusive
   flight deals and discounts. Don't forget to subscribe to our
   newsletters as well.

Let's book!

   Booking a ticket on BudgetAir.com.tw is very simple. With our clean and
   transparent website design, all you have to do when looking for a
   flight is to decide on where you want to go and on which travel dates.
   We will do the rest by sorting through the available flights and fares
   for those dates.

   You will find all available flights, prices, times and flight duration
   in the flight result page. Simply decide on which of those tickets you
   wish to book, then enter the passenger and payment details, confirm,
   and pay for your tickets. It's that simple!

